<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Auto Confirmation from Haigy</h1>
    <% if @order.is_guest_order %>
      <p>Dear Guest Customer,</p>
    <% else %>
      <p>Hello <%= @order.user.nickname %>,</p>
    <% end %>

    <br>
    <p>Thank you very much for shopping with us. Your order (<a href="https://haigy.com/#/order/<%= @order.secured_id %>/show"><%= @order.secured_id %></a>) has been successfully placed.</p>
    <p>You could click <a href="https://haigy.com/#/order/<%= @order.secured_id %>/show">here</a> to see your order details and status.</p>

    <br>
    <p>We hope to see you again soon.</p>
    <p>Haigy.com</p>
    <p><%= currentDateInPacificTime %></p>
  </body>
</html>